The features in this JavaScript code include:

The ability for players to challenge other players by entering a username
A function to update the game status and display it on the webpage
A function to handle the automatic roll of the dice after 30 seconds
A function to handle automatic forfeit of the game after 3 turns of inactivity
A function to handle manual forfeit of the game
A function to handle automatic payout to the winner
A function to update the leaderboard and display it on the webpage
A function to handle social media sharing, allowing players to share their win on social media platforms
A function to add mobile support for touch events
A function for input validation to ensure that the input entered by the player is valid
A function for error handling to catch and handle any errors that may occur during the execution of the code.
